                        werden von sölichen <expan>freyheit<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und
                                <expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, die wir von
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>vord<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<add><expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnedig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan></add>
<expan>selig<ex>er</ex></expan> gedechtnüzz in <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
                        landen und herscheften <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Also
                                <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir
                                <add><expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> ewrn gnaden
                                <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>will<ex>igen</ex></expan> dinst
                            <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan></add> die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gütlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>hören</expan> und <expan>gnediklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        von ew <expan>v<ex>er</ex>tige<ex>n</ex></expan> wöllet, als etc. Und das
                        etc. </ab>
</div>
